Did someone say triple-double?

@RyArch15 recorded the first triple-double of his career and second in Windy City franchise history with 14 points, 11 rebounds and 11 assists. Arch now has nine double-digit assist games this season. https://t.co/iSB13NXn5C
Have fun out there among the stars. https://t.co/S285MTwGtp
